race.comment: PURPLE ESPRIT (8) is third-up seeking the hat-trick off a comfortable win at Armidale. She raced a short-priced favourite in her last three and gets some weight relief. The extra metres assist and can finish hard. CRIMSON BONNET (10) disappointed in a CL3 at Scone but won a CL2 comfortably at Tamworth prior. That stacks up for this and fourth-up she's a decent chance to bounce. CHICKEN LEGS (5) also peaks and spiked his figures missing a whisker at Armidale. Tumbles in weight this level with a 3kg claim atop and that brings him into it. HE'S MY WARRIOR (6) came hard from the back beaten less than 1L in the same contest. On that effort he can't be ruled out.
